## Strategic Account Planning Workflow

- [ ] 1. Audit the current account relationship — what is and isn't working
- [ ] 2. Understand the client's business — their strategy, market position, competitive threats
- [ ] 3. Identify unmet needs and whitespace — where the client could be doing more
- [ ] 4. Map the agency's current service offerings to client needs
- [ ] 5. Identify growth opportunities — new services, expanded scope, new markets
- [ ] 6. Define strategic goals and success metrics for the account
- [ ] 7. Build a 12-month account roadmap with milestones and ownership

## Key Inputs
- Client account: {{client}}
- Current service scope: {{current_scope}}
- Client business context: {{business_context}}
- Agency relationship health: {{relationship_health}}
- Growth objectives: {{growth_objectives}}
